        "content": "<p>I thought I would share a simple example to colorise the terminal when printing test results. It's nothing fancy, but it might save you time looking for the codes and how to print them in Roc. I think they look cool!</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Elm\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">pass</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">withColor</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"PASS: \"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Green</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"nv\">fail</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">withColor</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"FAIL: \"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Red</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"kt\">Stdout</span><span class=\"nf\">.</span><span class=\"nv\">line</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"\\(pass)\\(name)\"</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Elm\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">interface</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">TerminalColor</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"nv\">exposes</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">Color</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">escape</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">withColor</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"nv\">imports</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[]</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"kt\">Color</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"kt\">Green</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"kt\">Red</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"kt\">Blue</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"kt\">Black</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"nv\">escape</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Color</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Str</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"nv\">escape</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">\\</span><span class=\"nv\">color</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"nv\">when</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">color</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">is</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kt\">Green</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"\\u(001b)[32m\"</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kt\">Red</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"\\u(001b)[31m\"</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kt\">Blue</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"\\u(001b)[34m\"</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kt\">Black</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"\\u(001b)[30m\"</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"err\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Resets</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">to</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">black</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">after</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"nv\">withColor</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Str</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Color</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Str</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"nv\">withColor</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">\\</span><span class=\"nv\">text</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">color</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"nv\">code</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">escape</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">color</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"nv\">black</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">escape</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">Black</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"\\(code)\\(text)\\(black)\"</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n</code></pre></div>",
